            <div type="transcript" id="J1671">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Judgment is justest</l>
                    <l>When the Judged</l>
                    <l>His action laid away</l>
                    <l>Divested is of every Disk</l>
                    <l>But his sincerity</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Honor is then the safest hue</l>
                    <l>In a posthumous Sun</l>
                    <l>Not any color will endure</l>
                    <l>That scrutiny can burn --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
